IMAPStore susede-remote
Account susede

MaildirStore susede-local
Path ~/.mail/susede/
Inbox ~/.mail/susede/inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel susede
Master :susede-remote:
Slave :susede-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

